\par\par \uc2 BUSSINESS\par \b \uc2 GOVT'S STRUCTURAL REFORMATION CREATES SUSTAINABLE  \highlight22\uc2 ECONOMY \highlight\uc2 : MINISTRY\b0\par\par\uc2 332 \uc2 words\par \uc2 18 October 2021\par \uc2 LKBN ANTARA\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2021. LKBN Antara \par \par \uc2 By\par \par \uc2 Jakarta (ANTARA) - Several structural reformation efforts undertake by the government are not only for facilitating recovery but also for creating a sustainable \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , according to Head of \b \highlight22\uc2 Fiscal Policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  at the Ministry of Finance Febrio Kacaribu.\par \par \uc2 During the talk on the 2022 State \b \highlight22\uc2 Budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  Webinar event here on Monday, Kacaribu outlined that this structural reformation comprised the formation of the Investment Management Institution (LPI), Job Creation Law, and Risk-based Online Single Submission (OSS).\par \par \uc2 These various reforms are crucial milestones in bolstering investment, increasing productivity, and creating quality jobs, he noted.\par \par \uc2 "We expect that it (structural reformation) could support \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth in future," Kacaribu stated.\par \par \uc2 Moreover, Indonesia"s \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is still potentially plagued by \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  in the next year due to the pandemic that has protracted in addition to the global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  trend.\par \par \uc2 To this end, Kacaribu will ensure that the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  next year would remain flexible and responsive in order to tackle that \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  as well as to mirror optimism and cautiousness.\par \par \uc2 Meanwhile, the theme of next year"s \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  -- \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery and structural reformation -- contains two key aspects, he highlighted.\par \par \uc2 Firstly, the 2022 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  is directed at handling the pandemic and conducting a gradual \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery.\par \par \uc2 Secondly, the 2022 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  is utilized to support structural reformation to drive growth acceleration and create a strong \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  in future.\par \par \uc2 "The 2022 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  is formulated by taking into account development goals, and it is based on the macro assumption that the government, along with the DPR (\b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 ), have agreed upon," Kacaribu expounded.\par \par \uc2 Meanwhile, he informed that Indonesia"s current \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth was recorded to be equal across all components and indicates an upward trend.\par \par \uc2 This is supported by \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  indicators, both in terms of consumption and production, that have shown an upward trend along with the bolstering of the pandemic-handling \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  by the government.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-FLI/A/S022/S022) 18-10-2021 17:47:16\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020211018ehai000m9\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
