\par\par \uc2 NATIONAL NEWS\par \b \uc2 NEED LAW ENFORCEMENT REFORMATION TO WELCOME SOCIETY 5.0: MK\b0\par\par\uc2 364 \uc2 words\par \uc2 31 October 2021\par \uc2 LKBN ANTARA\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2021. LKBN Antara \par \par \uc2 By\par \par \uc2 Jakarta (ANTARA) - Constitutional Court (MK) Justice Suhartoyo assessed that Indonesia should reform law enforcement in facing the challenges presented by Society 5.0.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CThe difference with conventional law enforcement is, in the Society 5.0 era, law enforcement is supported by the internet of things (IoT),\u8221\'20\'1D he said in the national online seminar titled \u8220\'20\'1CReflections on Indonesian Law Enforcement in the Era of Society 5.0" monitored from here, Sunday.\par \par \uc2 In the last two years, which is in line with the COVID-19 pandemic, the paradigm of life that was influenced by the Industrial Revolution 4.0 has shifted to Society 5.0, he said.\par \par \uc2 The Society 5.0 paradigm combines the Industrial Revolution 4.0 with initiatives to push development based on humanist values, he said.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CThe Society 5.0 is a paradigm that is developed to respond to global challenges, such as social and \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  inequality, depleting natural resources, terrorism, pandemic, \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 , and complexity at almost all level of life," Suhartoyo expounded.\par \par \uc2 For that reason, Society 5.0 will develop a human-centred society by balancing \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth to eliminate inequality and solving social problems by using a system that integrates cyberspace and physical space.\par \par \uc2 Regarding law enforcement that is more human-oriented, he opined that law enforcement reformation should be conducted in several aspects, namely betterment in the use of fair law as the basis for good decision making by state apparatus and requiring judicial institutions to maintain the principles of independence, impartiality, and freedom in making decisions.\par \par \uc2 Aside from that, he noted that Society 5.0 also requires law enforcement reformation that is related to increasing the professionalism of law enforcement officers, law enforcement that is based on the principles of justice, law enforcement that prioritizes the promotion and protection of human rights, as well as increasing \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  participation and supervision mechanism to be more effective.\par \par \uc2 "On the other hand, the law can also hinder the development of innovation. Therefore, the preparation of future regulations must be helpful to the innovation itself," the justice said.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-RAP/A/S022/S022) 31-10-2021 18:48:33\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020211031ehav000gp\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
