inued to expand, as reflected in Indonesia"s Purchasing Manager Index (PMI) in October 2021, at 57.2 points or higher than 51 recorded during the period before the pandemic.\par \par \uc2 "Data shows that demand already exists and is getting better. With the growth in demand, manufacturing facilities, factories, and industries must boost their production to meet the demand," Jokowi affirmed.\par \par \uc2 Other attendees at the PTBI Annual Meeting were Coordinating Minister for \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Affairs Airlangga Hartarto, Minister of Finance \uc2 Sri Mulyani Indrawati\uc2 , Minister of Trade Muhammad Lutfi, Chairman of the Board of Commissioners of the \uc2 Financial Services Authority (OJK) \uc2 Wimboh Santoso, Chairman of the Board of Commissioners of the Deposit Insurance Corporation (LPS) Purbaya Yudhi Sadewa, and other relevant officials.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-RST/A/H-FDH/H-FDH) 24-11-2021 15:47:53\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020211124ehbo000jh\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw177\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2655\pichgoal600
