\par\par \b \uc2 Law without credibility\b0\par\par\uc2 537 \uc2 words\par \uc2 29 November 2021\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 6\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2021 The Jakarta Post \par \par \uc2 The Jakarta Post,\par \par \uc2 For sure, the Constitutional Court's order on Thursday for the government to amend the controversial Job Creation Law in two years, or else it will be declared unconstitutional, marks a setback for President Joko "Jokowi" Widodo's administration's bid to cut red tape and bring in investments that would create jobs. Domestic and overseas investors will consequently put their business plans on hold until the legal \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  is settled, if not look for other opportunities elsewhere.\par \par \uc2 But as the court said in its narrowly split decision -- five in favor of the plaintiffs versus four against -- the omnibus law was considered flawed because of its \b \highlight22\uc2 legislative\b0 \highlight\uc2  procedure that ran counter the Constitution. Last-minute changes were made to the final draft that was endorsed by the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 , while there were mistakes in the \b \highlight22\uc2 legislation\b0 \highlight\uc2 's citations of nearly 80 existing laws that it removed.\par \par \uc2 More than that, both the government and lawmakers turned a deaf ear to \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  voices and concerns critical of the draft bill throughout the deliberation process. Under the pretext of health protocols to contain the spread of COVID-19, crucial parts of the debate were held behind closed doors and rallies to protest the bill were quelled.\par \par \uc2 The strong message the court is sending is that next time we rush \b \highlight22\uc2 legislation\b0 \highlight\uc2 , through bypassing the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  consultation, the \b \highlight22\uc2 legislation\b0 \highlight\uc2  will end up in the court and we are back to the drawing board. But this is how democracy works in contemporary Indonesia, where the opposition, hence the checks and balances mechanism, is not functioning.\par \par \uc2 With the ruling coalition controlling more than 80 percent of the House seats, there is a temptation for the government to bulldoze its way through the \b \highlight22\uc2 legislative\b0 \highlight\uc2  process as in the case of the jobs law. Thanks to the Constitutional Court, we can hope for the safeguarding of our hard-won democracy.\par \par \uc2 We should have no qualm the \b \highlight22\uc2 legislation\b0 \highlight\uc2  was drafted in good faith. Even before the COVID-19 pandemic, Indonesia performed disappointingly in terms of productivity and competitiveness compared with fellow developing nations thanks in part to our regulatory problems. The \uc2 Organization for \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Cooperation and Development\uc2  (\uc2 OECD\uc2 ), for example, classified Indonesia among one of the most restrictive countries to foreign direct investment because of its many man-made barriers.\par \par \uc2 The omnibus law wasenvisioned as a panacea, but goals cannot simply justify the means. It is therefore heartening that the government has accepted the court's decision and will soon begin amending the law. This may show respect for the rule of law on the government's part, but it is not enough.\par \par \uc2 Not only does the government have to stop issuing implementing regulations of the jobs law, but it has to make sure the revision of the law follows the proper mechanism, which includes adequate consultation with the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  given the overarching impacts of the law on them and the environment.\par \par \uc2 The recent judicial review is not the first challenge to the legitimacy of the Job Creation Law, as there are other petitions against the omnibus law with the Constitutional Court. While this may undermine business and legal certainty, we have learned why good law-making procedures must stand.\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020211128ehbt0000d\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
