mic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery," he explained.\par \par \uc2 Warjiyo noted that the five \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  responses of BI comprised the transformation of the real sector, including the downstreaming of natural resources, which also responded to global challenges to the green \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 Second, the synergy between the Ministry of Finance and BI regarding \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  and monetary policies in order to maintain macroeconomic stability and jointly restore the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 Third, BI, along with KSSK, encouraged credit and financing from the financial sector banking to the real sector of the business world, from the demand and supply side.\par \par \uc2 The fourth response is the digitalization of the national financial \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  in accordance with President Jokowi"s direction and the last \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  response is developing and building an inclusive and green financial \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 "That is our answer to prudence in an effort to ensure the prospects of \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery will rise and recover. Synergy and innovation in national \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery," he noted.\par \par \uc2 BI"s \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  in 2022 is focused on continuing to encourage \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery with synergies among the government, KSSK, and related stakeholders.\par \par \uc2 "The monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is aimed at responding to the increasing global \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," he expounded.\par \par \uc2 In addition, BI remains committed to maintaining exchange rate stability and ensuring better liquidity in the banking system.\par \p