\par\par \uc2 BUSSINESS\par \b  \highlight22\uc2 PUBLIC \highlight\uc2  MUST MITIGATE PANDEMIC-TRIGGERED GLOBAL  \highlight22\uc2 UNCERTAINTY \highlight\uc2 : VP AMIN\b0\par\par\uc2 344 \uc2 words\par \uc2 7 December 2021\par \uc2 LKBN ANTARA\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2021. LKBN Antara \par \par \uc2 By\par \par \uc2 Jakarta (ANTARA) - Vice President Ma"ruf Amin reminded residents to be alert and take precautionary measures amid protracted \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  due to the COVID-19 pandemic that continues to loom large over the global community.\par \par \uc2 "We need to be cautious, as global \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  due to the COVID-19 pandemic remains high," the vice president noted in his keynote speech at the Institute of Indonesia Chartered Accountants\u8217\'20\'19 (IAI"s) 64th anniversary commemoration webinar here on Tuesday.\par \par \uc2 Amin encouraged residents to continue to pursue self-sufficiency for the nation to face the post-COVID-19 pandemic era.\par \par \uc2 "We want to achieve national self-sufficiency and resilience to face the post-pandemic era," he remarked.\par \par \uc2 The nation must achieve self-sufficiency in the areas of \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , social, culture, climate change, and other key sectors, Amin stated.\par \par \uc2 "We must also maintain our active role in global leadership, especially as Indonesia assumes the G20 presidency for the next year," the vice president added.\par \par \uc2 Amin also encouraged chartered accountants to play an active role in national development by promoting an adaptive work standard relevant to likely changes in the future.\par \par \uc2 "Mastery over technology is no longer a choice but a requirement for a professional accountant," Amin stated.\par \par \uc2 Challenges and fluctuating situations faced by chartered accountants during their duty would hone their competence, for which work orientation and governance are paramount to nurture a professional work character, the vice president stated.\par \par \uc2 Amin suggested charted accountants to enhance their personal integrity and work quality, competence, and experience to maintain solid \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  confidence in their profession.\par \par \uc2 Amin also pushed the chartered accountant association to take on a broader role to develop the Islamic \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and financial system in Indonesian regions.\par \par \uc2 "I urge IAI and IAI members to focus on issues that attract \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  attention, such as development of the Islamic \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and financial system as well as the micro, small, and middle-scale enterprises (MSMEs)," the vice president remarked.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-NBL/B/H-FDH/H-FDH) 07-12-2021 14:55:39\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020211207ehc7000dx\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
