\par\par \uc2 BUSSINESS\par \b \uc2 INDONESIA'S  \highlight22\uc2 TAX \highlight\uc2  REVENUES SURPASSED TARGET UNTIL DEC 26: FINANCE MINISTER\b0\par\par\uc2 450 \uc2 words\par \uc2 27 December 2021\par \uc2 LKBN ANTARA\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2021. LKBN Antara \par \par \uc2 By\par \par \uc2 Jakarta (ANTARA) - \b \highlight22\uc2 Tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues until December 26, 2021, had reached Rp 1,231.87 trillion, or 100.19 percent of the target mandated in the State-\b \highlight22\uc2 Budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  (APBN) for the 2021 \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  year, according to Finance Minister \uc2 Sri Mulyani Indrawati\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 "Until December 26, 2021, the net \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue amounted to Rp1,231.87 trillion. This figure is equal to 100.19 percent of the target mandated in the 2021 APBN \b \highlight22\uc2 Fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  Year of Rp1,229.6 trillion," Indrawati said in an official statement on Monday.\par \par \uc2 The minister also lauded and thanked the work of the Directorate General of \b \highlight22\uc2 Taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  (DJP) for the achievement in 2021.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CToday is a historic day, amid the COVID-19 pandemic, while the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is still recovering, we are able to achieve 100-percent \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue. I express my gratitude and appreciation to DJP," she affirmed.\par \par \uc2 Indrawati remarked that the achievement of \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues in 2021 is a provision to fulfill the subsequent tasks of the Finance Ministry in future.\par \par \uc2 Furthermore, the DJP recorded that 138 \b \highlight22\uc2 Tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  Service Offices (KPP) across Indonesia had exceeded the target of each KPP.\par \par \uc2 In addition, \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues in the seven Regional Offices (Kanwil) had also reached over 100 percent of the target set for each Regional Office.\par \par \uc2 The regional offices are the South Jakarta I DJP Regional Office, the Large Taxpayer DJP Regional Office, the Special Jakarta DJP Regional Office, the Central Sulawesi DJP Regional Office, the North Sulawesi DJP Regional Office, Gorontalo DJP Regional Office, and North Maluku DJP Regional Office.\par \par \uc2 The West Kalimantan DJP Regional Office, South and Central Kalimantan DJP Regional Offices, and North Jakarta DJP Regional Office were the other regional offices.\par \par \uc2 Director General of \b \highlight22\uc2 Taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  Suryo Utomo believes this success could not be separated from the participation of taxpayers and the hard work of over 46 thousand DJP employees to exceed the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue target after 12 years.\par \par \uc2 However, Utomo noted that the euphoria regarding this success should not be excessive. In future, the challenge will be tougher since the APBN \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  exceeding three percent of the gross domestic product (GDP) is only permitted until 2022.\par \par \uc2 Concurrently, \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  triggered by the COVID-19 pandemic continues to loom large. State revenues are also demanded to be bigger to return the APBN \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  in 2023 back to below three percent of the GDP.\par \par \uc2 "Hence, the DJP will continue to evaluate the performance in 2021 to prepare for a better output in 2022. We will continue our good performance and strategies in 2022 while replacing poor performance and strategies," he affirmed.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-RST/A/H-FDH/H-FDH) 27-12-2021 20:44:34\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020211227ehcr001md\par }\par \b \uc2 Search Summary\b0\par \par  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx2000\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrd